cc:Work.dc:description:
Shoe shaped box
Shoe shaped box with flat sides and rounded top. Works best if flex if under slight compression. Make sure that the following conditions are met: y > tophole + r + fronttop; height > frontheight.
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes Shoe Command line short: boxes Shoe
